ğŸ”¹ Divisibility Rules (Must Remember)

Divisible by 2 â†’ last digit even

Divisible by 3 â†’ sum of digits divisible by 3

Divisible by 5 â†’ last digit 0 or 5

Divisible by 9 â†’ sum of digits divisible by 9

